    <FlavorTextDef>
        <InternalName>FIRST_CONTACT_MAIN</InternalName>
        <FlavorTextOption>
            <Requirements>
                <SpeakerFaction>FACTION_ALTARIAN</SpeakerFaction>
                <ListenerRaceTrait>ExterminatorsAbility</ListenerRaceTrait>
            </Requirements>
            <Text>Your arrival fills us with deep concern. Your reputation precedes you, a shadow cast across the stars, a symbol of unbridled malevolence and destruction.[BR][BR]Our civilization, guided by principles of enlightenment and harmony, stands in stark contrast to your ruthless ethos. The Korath's blatant disregard for life, for the sanctity of sentient existence, is an abomination in our eyes.</Text>
