    <FlavorTextDef>
        <InternalName>FIRST_CONTACT_MAIN</InternalName>
        <FlavorTextOption>
            <Requirements>
                <SpeakerFaction>FACTION_TORIAN</SpeakerFaction>
                <ListenerRaceTrait>ExterminatorsAbility</ListenerRaceTrait>
            </Requirements>
            <Text>Our people, the Torians, and our memory of suffering at the hands of monsters like you is long and bitter. Your kind, with your contemptuous view of other species as mere tools, embodies the very essence of our disdain. [BR][BR]We are acutely aware of the atrocities you commit, the abhorrent genetic manipulations to create docile, ruined beings, treating sentient life as cattle. Such acts are not just aggressive; they are an affront to the very essence of what it means to be sentient. [BR][BR]We will not go quietly into the night.
                </Text>
            <PreferenceWeight>100000</PreferenceWeight>
        </FlavorTextOption>
