                <ListenerRaceTrait>ExterminatorsAbility</ListenerRaceTrait>
            </Requirements>
            <Text>We greet you with a nod of equal stature, yet with eyes wide open to your true nature. Your strength is undeniable.[BR][BR]We recognize you as a formidable player. Like us, you understand the necessity of asserting dominance. While you wield brute force, for that suits your limited capabilities, we prefer the subtlety of manipulation, the art of steering events from the shadows.</Text>
